# Demo Web Shop – UI Automation Project

This project is a basic Selenium TestNG automation framework that verifies the scroll functionality on [demowebshop.tricentis.com](https://demowebshop.tricentis.com).

## 📌 What This Project Does:
- Searches for a product using the homepage search box
- Scrolls to the bottom of the page using JavaScriptExecutor
- Verifies that the footer section is visible after scroll
- Implements Page Object Model (POM) structure

## 🧰 Tools & Tech Used:
- Java
- Selenium WebDriver
- TestNG
- Maven
- WebDriverManager
- Page Object Model (POM)
- Git + GitHub

## ✅ How to Run:
- Clone this repo  
- Open it in your IDE (Eclipse or IntelliJ)  
- Run `mvn test` in terminal  
- Or right-click and run `NavigationFlowTest.java` with TestNG

## 🧪 Project Status:
✅ Fully working  
🚫 Cart-related flow intentionally excluded due to inconsistent site behavior (DOM instability)

